{"word":"G2185 - ἐφικνέομαι - ephiknéomai - ef-ik-neh'-om-ahee - Reach","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐφικνέομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ephiknéomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ef-ik-neh'-om-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Reach</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வந்தெட்டு"},{"paragraph":"1. to come to"},{"paragraph":"2. to reach"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1909 - ἐπί - epí - ep-ee'/1909\">G1909</a> and a cognate of <a href=\"#/G2240 - ἥκω - hḗkō - hay'-ko/2240\">G2240</a>; to arrive <i>upon</i>, that is, <i>extend to:</i> - reach.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}